Game : Slave Zero 
Date : 2004/08/22 
Video: PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped 

500 years into the future and the SovKhan are in control.  Only the "Guardians" and thier Mech Units can stop them. You take control of Chan his mech Slave Zero in a bid to blast your way through Meagcity S1-9. Using your upgradable weapons dodge & blast your your way to the bosses and rescue the planet. Or get a friend and blow them away in the multiplayer game. Enjoy!